description: Cha Cha Chow is the new food truck in St. Louis establishing a revolution in "Street Dining". We are professionally trained, locally grown, and we are fired up about bringing our COMPLETELY HOMEMADE menu to you.Mobile and not afraid to use it, we aren't your ordinary food truck. We cook EVERYTHING on board and have a big window to show it.That means we gotta deliver fresh, we gotta do quality, we gotta blow your mind with flavors, and we gotta be faster than a Japanese bullet train.Step out of the ordinary and strap on some nouveaux dining that's blazing a trail through St. Louis.VIVA LA CHA CHA!
name: Cha Cha Chow
